prompts.frontCover:
A dynamic and action-packed comic book cover featuring cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo. They are depicted as a superhero duo, "The Dynamic Duo of Deliciousness." Lao Lao is in a heroic pose, using giant chopsticks like superpowers to expertly catch flying pieces of sushi that are raining down from the sky. Jordan is next to her, striking a triumphant pose, holding a leash attached to two adorable cartoon dogs (a Shiba Inu and a Corgi) who are wearing tiny superhero capes and happily catching falling edamame beans in their mouths. The background is a vibrant, explosive cityscape with classic comic book "POW!" and "YUM!" sound effect bubbles. The overall scene is filled with energy, bold colors, halftone dots, and thick black outlines typical of vintage comics.

Centered in the middle of the composition, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my Super Girlfriend, Lao Lao!"
